{"title":"炼塔和人","authors":["潘烽"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":7,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼塔和人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潘烽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完成一个崛起的造型"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧马人不用长鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驯服了蛮横"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有花儿开放了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可这季节依旧太冷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常是真心地笑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫不经心擦去腮边的泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拎一个沉袋子来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷一个空口袋而去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷冷热热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看天空的一处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有火焰起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的光在蔓延"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远保持着沉默"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还需要什么哪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要一把竹笛就够了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今晚的月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会早早地升起"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}